---
title: Garlic & Honey Chicken with Roast Oregano Veggie Salad & Crumbly Cheese
description: The combination of garlic and honey infuses this colourful meal for a flavoursome result that comes together with
minimal effort. Top it off with smokey aioli and crumbly cheese for a 5-star finish.

